Living Off the Land Binaries (LOLBins) Overview:
===============================================

LOLBins are legitimate system binaries that can be abused by attackers to:
1. Execute malicious code
2. Download files
3. Bypass application whitelisting
4. Perform reconnaissance
5. Maintain persistence

Common LOLBins Categories:
- File Operations: certutil.exe, bitsadmin.exe
- Code Execution: regsvr32.exe, rundll32.exe, mshta.exe
- Network Operations: curl.exe, wget (Linux)
- System Information: wmic.exe, systeminfo.exe
- Scripting: powershell.exe, cscript.exe, wscript.exe

Benefits for Red Teams:
- Blend in with normal system activity
- Bypass application whitelisting
- Avoid detection by security tools
- Use trusted, signed binaries
EOF

